description:
Is Ellen White a false prophet or does she meet the criteria of a true prophet? How do we know? Do Christians have to believe in her to go to Heaven? Walter Veith outlines the Biblical criteria of how to identify a real prophet. God used prophets to call those out of ignorance and to teach them about God. The criteria includes how a prophet must be in harmony with the Word, must speak the truth, and others. Hear about how Ellen White has met the qualifications of a prophet according to the Bible. 

For more please visit: http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/c/95/Bible Answers/
